	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64191232"><p>Vendors are also customers, depending on which relationships you are looking at.</p><p>Developers are vendors to the users of the software they develop, yes. Those developers also pay Apple fees and commissions to have their apps made available in the App Store. They pay Apple for payment processing and customer service. As such, they are customers of Apple.</p><p>The relationship under scrutiny here by the EU is the relationship between developers and Apple (where developers are the customers), not the relationship betw<span class="substr"> </span></p></div>
	</div>

